  "texts": [
    "APPENDIX B ADDITIONAL VISUALIZATION B.1 Structure of Magic Text-EncoderThe structure of the Magic Text-Encoder, depicted in Fig. 26, comprises the original CLIP Text Encoder and several newly added convolutional layers L 1 and L 2.",
    "During the training process, only the newly added modules (e.g., L 1 and L 2) are trained; subsequently, the results are weighted and combined with the output of the CLIP Text Encoder X 0.",
    "B.2 Samples from the ChronoMagic DatasetIn this work, we compiled a collection of time-lapse videos from the Internet to create a metamorphic video-text dataset containing 2,265 videos, named the ChronoMagic.",
    "Fig. 23, Fig.",
    "21 and Fig. 22 showcases statistics and samples from the dataset, which primarily consists of metamorphic timelapse videos of plants, buildings, ice, food, and other categories."
  ]
}